descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 15 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

#                                                                                                                                                                                                       
[media]

# "Totally Cooked" Update Available Now!

Burning food, fire-breathing customers, and explosive tools await you! Can you handle the heat?

[media]

# Prepare With Care 
Use your trusty kitchen tools to slice, flip, and serve. Don't burn the fries! 
[media]

# Crazy Cooking
Gourmet customers will have extraordinary orders, so make sure to satisfy their tastes!
[media]

# Set Up For Success 
Customize all aspects of your truck's layout to optimize performance. Your truck, your rules!
[media]

# Gourmet Glow Up 
Buy new trucks, upgrade your equipment, and challenge your cooking skills while discovering something new!
[media]
